<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.1">
<l>kaṭaṉñālañ ceytēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kaṭaṉñāla māvēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kaṭaṉñālaṅ koṇṭēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ 	kaṭaṉñālaṅ kīṇṭēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kaṭaṉñāla muṇṭēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kaṭaṉñālat tīcaṉvan tēṟak kolō</l>
<l>kaṭaṉñā lattīrk kivaiyeṉ collukēṉ kaṭaṉñā latteṉ makaḷkaṟ kiṉṟaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“I have made the sea[-girded] world”, she says,</l>
	<l>“I am the sea[-girded] world”, she says,</l>
<l>“I have taken the sea[-girded] world”, she says,</l>
	<l>“I have split the sea[-girded] world”, she says,</l>
<l>“I have eaten the sea[-girded] world”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the lord of the sea[-girded] world settles in [her]?</l>
<l>Why will I say these [words] to you of the sea[-girded]  world,</l>
	<l>[words also] learned by my daughter of the sea[-girded] world?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
